{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"88cdf5247a","title":"中共中央关于各地给中央来电及报告应写全名的通知","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1bea1cdab2","index":0,"year":1968,"month":2,"day":16,"articleId":"88cdf5247a"}],"tags":[{"id":"1d084c925f","name":"革命委员会","type":"主题"},{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"318138ea26","name":"重要党政机构及其衍变","type":"主题"},{"id":"3df4ae75e1","name":"干部和干部政策","type":"主题"},{"id":"91736a0628","name":"中共中央通知","type":"发行机构"},{"id":"ef6e778547","name":"中央文件","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f9e88f574b","type":"title","text":"中共中央关于各地给中央来电及报告应写全名的通知","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"88cdf5247a"},{"id":"0c6d49b227","type":"paragraph","text":"各省、市、自治区革命委员会（革筹小组）、军管会、各大军区、省军区、各野战军：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"88cdf5247a"},{"id":"27117166bc","type":"paragraph","text":"今后，各地给中央的一般性政治性来电和报告，应写全名为：《毛主席、林副主席、中央、国务院、中央军委、中央文革》。如有专题需向中央请示的，属于无产阶级文化大革命和党的问题，可电告中央、中央文革；属于军事问题，可电告中央军委；属于行政业务问题，可电告国务院。此外，不要给个人来电，丧失组织原则，以免难于处理。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"88cdf5247a"},{"id":"8d2be745e8","type":"paragraph","text":"中共中央","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"88cdf5247a"},{"id":"4c2ce802e3","type":"paragraph","text":"国务院","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"88cdf5247a"},{"id":"4f405a2134","type":"paragraph","text":"中央军委","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"88cdf5247a"},{"id":"653efc399b","type":"paragraph","text":"中央文革","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"88cdf5247a"},{"id":"f245020b95","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六八年二月十六日","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"88cdf5247a"}],"page":{"id":"1bb071da88","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"88cdf5247a","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}